[OVERLAY] VimFu — The \ Key
[SAY] Backslash is the leader key. It does nothing alone. It's a prefix for custom mappings you define.
[SAY] Map leader W to save the file.
[TYPE] ':nnoremap \\w :w<CR>\n'

